CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 9, 1952, pg. 19 reads: Baby Blessed - Baby William Strothers Jr. was blessed at the Mount Ararat Baptist Church by the Rev. C.A. Burrell on Sunday, Feb. 3. Standing, left to right: Stewart W. Strothers, godfather; Mrs. Cester Nicholas, godmother, nad Mr. and Mrs. William L. Strothers, parents.  A dinner in honor of the church blessings was held later the same day at the home of the maternal grandparents, Mr. and Mrs. J.B.Reid, 3138 Avalon Street.  Attending, in addition to those in picture, were Mr. and Mrs. Stewart L. Strothers Sr., paternal grandparents; Mrs. Helen Luckey and Gerald Strothers. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of William Strothers Jr. lying on sofa in home of Mr. and Mrs. J.B. Reid, 3138 Avalon Street
